    {
      "id": "PopularPost167608",
      "post_content": "I've never really like the Radiance keyword, which is a shame because I really like R/W. Here, this spell can be rather powerful, but there's been plenty of times where casting this would untap my opponent's creatures and boost them as well.  \n  \nIf it was simply \"creatures you control\", I'd be much more willing to play this card. In a way, I prefer [Fortify](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fortify), but overall this card's slot ended up being taken by [Glory of Warfare](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glory of Warfare).  \n  \nNice art and flavor though.",
      "posted_by": "Asmodi0000",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost167608\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">I've never really like the Radiance keyword, which is a shame because I really like R/W. Here, this spell can be rather powerful, but there's been plenty of times where casting this would untap my opponent's creatures and boost them as well.<br/><br/>If it was simply \"creatures you control\", I'd be much more willing to play this card. In a way, I prefer <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fortify\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fortify\">Fortify</a>, but overall this card's slot ended up being taken by <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Glory of Warfare\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glory of Warfare\">Glory of Warfare</a>.<br/><br/>Nice art and flavor though.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '167608'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy18984\">Asmodi0000</span>\r\n                                (6/9/2011 5:49:03 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubC